</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>Binance 曾暫停運作，令 Bitcoin 跌穿 2.1 萬美元</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/06/14/binance-4/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=binance-4</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[EMMA]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 14 Jun 2022 11:22:16 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1104600</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>加密貨幣借貸平臺 Celsius Networks LLC 及加密貨幣交易所 Binance 日前相繼發生事故 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>加密貨幣借貸平臺 Celsius Networks LLC 及加密貨幣交易所 Binance 日前相繼發生事故，Binance 因「交易受阻」關係，突然暫停用戶提取加密貨幣，但經搶救數小時後己恢復正常。而消息曾引致加密貨幣市場波動，Bitcoin 曾跌穿 $21,000 美元。</p><p>Binance 創辦人兼 CEO 趙長鵬於 Twitter 發表推文表示，平臺因某筆交易導致提取 Bitcoin（比特幣）網路面臨積壓問題，因此只能暫停運作，但相信可在 30 分鐘內恢復。他又強調資金已受「投資者保護基金」（SAFU）保障，用戶不會有所損失。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Temporary pause of <a href="https://twitter.com/search?q=%24BTC&amp;src=ctag&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">$BTC</a> withdrawals on <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Binance?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Binance</a> due to a stuck transaction causing a backlog. Should be fixed in ~30 minutes. Will update.</p><p>Funds are SAFU.</p><p>&mdash; CZ 🔶 Binance (@cz_binance) <a href="https://twitter.com/cz_binance/status/1536317704990208000?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">June 13, 2022</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>但 Binance 其他在官方 Twitter 表示，暫停用提取的時間將延長 3 小時，但此狀況隻影響 Bitcoin 網路提取，用戶仍可透過其他網路如 BEP-20 正常提取貨幣，存款不受影響。Binance 又解釋，事件由於 TX（TransferCoin ）費用低，一批 Bitcoin 交易被阻礙，導致 Bitcoin 網絡提款積壓。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">A batch of <a href="https://twitter.com/search?q=%24BTC&amp;src=ctag&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">$BTC</a> transactions got stuck due to low TX fees, resulting in a backlog of BTC network withdrawals.</p><p>As a result, withdrawals on the Bitcoin network are temporarily suspended on Binance.</p><p>BTC withdrawals on other networks (BEP20 &amp; ERC20) remain open as normal.</p><p>&mdash; Binance (@binance) <a href="https://twitter.com/binance/status/1536337215877283840?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">June 13, 2022</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>而 Celsius 於透過官方網誌表示，由於市場出現極端狀況，已暫停讓用戶提款、交換及帳戶間轉帳，並稱此乃穩定流動性及營運的必要行動。與此同時，公司正設法保留並保護資產。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1104666 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/287055742_709086266865941_6437275590768359214_n-694x409.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="409" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/287055742_709086266865941_6437275590768359214_n-694x409.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/287055742_709086266865941_6437275590768359214_n-768x452.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/287055742_709086266865941_6437275590768359214_n.jpg 949w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p class="p1"><span class="s1">據</span> <span class="s2">Coinbase 網站</span>顯示，Bitcoin 曾一度於今日（14 日）上午十時<span class="s1">跌至</span> $20,816.40 <span class="s1">美元</span>，是至 2020 年 12 月以來的最低水平。<span class="s1">截至現時為止，Bitcoin 逐步回升至＄22,905 美元。</span></p><p class="p1"><span class="s1">資料</span><span class="s2">來源：<a href="https://www.cnbc.com/2022/06/13/binance-pauses-bitcoin-withdrawals-as-crypto-sell-off-deepens.html">cnbc</a></span>、<a href="https://www.coinbase.com/price/bitcoin"><span class="s2">Coinbase</span></a>，<a href="https://technews.tw/2022/06/14/binance-stuck-transaction/">Technews.tw</a></p><p class="p1">—</p><p class="p2"><span class="s3">unwire.hk</span> Mewe <span class="s4">專頁：</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span class="s3">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width=