</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>臺灣車手被紫外線消毒燈嚴重燙傷　 眼角膜受損+雙腳燒傷</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/06/14/uvlight/hottopic/spotlight/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=uvlight</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Natalie]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 14 Jun 2022 06:59:19 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[城中熱話]]></category><category><![CDATA[紫外線燈]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1104591</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>經過 5 波的疫情後，現時我們都十分著緊個人衛生，時常都要消毒家居避免「中招」，但消毒工具的安全性亦不容忽視。 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">經過 5 波的疫情後，現時我們都十分著緊個人衛生，時常都要消毒家居避免「中招」，但消毒工具的安全性亦不容忽視。有名臺灣網紅則在使用紫外線消毒燈後，意外將自己雙腳及眼角膜造成嚴重燒傷，需要送院進行緊急治療。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1104592" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/287569728_3049865798610864_134062298814833493_n-694x520.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="520" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/287569728_3049865798610864_134062298814833493_n-694x520.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/287569728_3049865798610864_134062298814833493_n-1202x900.jpeg 1202w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/287569728_3049865798610864_134062298814833493_n-768x575.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/287569728_3049865798610864_134062298814833493_n.jpeg 1440w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">日前，臺灣汽車界網紅「Andy 老爹」打算使用紫外線燈消毒家居，但經過 3 小時後，其雙腳及眼睛都嚴重燒傷，整個小腿紅腫脫皮，眼睛通紅，更曾一度打不開雙眼。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1104593" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/286410333_3049865835277527_5820076117356487934_n-434x580.jpeg" alt="" width="434" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/286410333_3049865835277527_5820076117356487934_n-434x580.jpeg 434w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/286410333_3049865835277527_5820076117356487934_n-674x900.jpeg 674w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/286410333_3049865835277527_5820076117356487934_n-768x1026.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/286410333_3049865835277527_5820076117356487934_n.jpeg 1078w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 434px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1104594" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/286356664_3049865858610858_2357569156012376072_n-435x580.jpeg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/286356664_3049865858610858_2357569156012376072_n-435x580.jpeg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/286356664_3049865858610858_2357569156012376072_n-675x900.jpeg 675w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/286356664_3049865858610858_2357569156012376072_n-768x1024.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/286356664_3049865858610858_2357569156012376072_n.jpeg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">經治療後，「Andy 老爹」在 Facebook 發文自嘲自己被包紥得「像木乃伊一樣」，更呼籲網民要小心使用紫外線燈，以免遇上同樣意外，他指：「</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">所以提醒大家紫外線殺菌燈使用真的要小心&#8230;.當然我自己本身不知道威力有這麼強，才會這麼蠢的使用，也提醒大家&#8230;.千萬要小心&#8230;.</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">」</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1104595" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/287492663_3049865818610862_8545801695116029804_n-694x520.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="520" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/287492663_3049865818610862_8545801695116029804_n-694x520.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/287492663_3049865818610862_8545801695116029804_n-1202x900.jpeg 1202w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/287492663_3049865818610862_8545801695116029804_n-768x575.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/287492663_3049865818610862_8545801695116029804_n.jpeg 1440w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1104596" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/286312261_3049865808610863_5068994546836265510_n-694x520.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="520" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/286312261_3049865808610863_5068994546836265510_n-694x520.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/286312261_3049865808610863_5068994546836265510_n-1202x900.jpeg 1202w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/286312261_3049865808610863_5068994546836265510_n-768x575.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/286312261_3049865808610863_5068994546836265510_n.jpeg 1440w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/andyplaycar/posts/3049865908610853">Andy 老爹 Facebook </a></span></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;theme=light&amp;color=white&amp;controls=0&amp;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><div class="feedflare">
